1. Create  an S3  bucket for Hosting 

1.Log into the AWS console and search for S3
   >>Create bucket
  *Bucket name: must be global and unique
  *Region: Choose closest to your user
  *Uncheck "block all public access"[we will configure policies manually]
  *Enable versioning [for backup]

2.Upload your website files to the Bucket
  
3.Enable static website files hosting
  *Go to properties  -> enable Static Website hosting
  *Select Enable
  *Index document: index.html
  *error document: error.html(optional)


 


